The paper deals with distributed statistical learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper discusses the trade-off between communication and computation in distributed learning, which is a common theme in the field of distributed computing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
